  triage:title "TraitOnly visibility variant and nullable BoundaryRecord fields missing from schema contract" ;
  triage:description "The schema contract for boundary loading on feature/sprint-A6 is partially implemented. Specifically: (1) the TraitOnly visibility variant is absent from the VisibilityKind enum or equivalent type, and (2) BoundaryRecord fields that the contract specifies as nullable (Option<T>) are not nullable in the implementation. Sprint A.6 acceptance criteria require the complete schema contract. Fix: add TraitOnly to the visibility enum and make the appropriate BoundaryRecord fields Option<T> per the sprint-A6.md schema spec." ;
